        <p>The NCS Group offers a complete spectrum of project-based services to our Clients. Whether completing a previously installed project, auditing and recovering a project in difficulty, consulting with our Client's project management staff, or setting up and operating a project (program) management office, The NCS Group has the structure, knowledge, and experience to get the job done.
<br>........................................................................................<br><br>
